Summary

Dataset: Malawi

Outcome variable: Kaufman number recall at Endline (nr1 - nr22)

Comparison variable: Gender (Male, Female)

Items with no variance: a nr17, nr18, nr19, nr20, nr21, nr22

Items with no variance within levels of comparison variable: b nr16

Bias detection method: IRT

Total number of biased items: 0 out of 22

Type of item bias: NA

a Items were not included in any DIF analysis and were not used to compute IRT-based robustness checks of treatment effects.

b Items were not included in the IRT-based DIF analysis and were not used to compute IRT-based robustness checks of treatment effects.

No DIF was detected by IRT. Therefore, robustness checks of treatment effects were not performed.
